### 2. MatchdayHero (Home Pattern)

Diagonal split hero with MVP highlight and stats.

```tsx
<MatchdayHero
  data={{
    competition: 'Brasileirão · Round 14',
    statusPrimary: 'Final',
    statusSecondary: 'Victory',
    statusVariant: 'preview',
    solidYellow: true,  // Full yellow background (no split)
    home: { short: 'FLA', name: 'Flamengo', score: 2, crestUrl: '...' },
    away: { short: 'PAL', name: 'Palmeiras', score: 1, crestUrl: '...' },
    stats: [
      { label: 'Victories', value: '8' },
      { label: 'Draws', value: '3' },
    ],
    highlight: {
      name: 'Gabriel Barbosa',
      number: 9,
      quote: 'Two goals in 15 minutes.',
      photoUrl: '...',
    },
    actions: [
      { label: 'View postgame', href: '/postgame', variant: 'primary' },
    ],
    scrollCueTargetId: 'home-below-fold',
  }}
/>
```

**Features:**
- Diagonal split 62/38 (desktop) with `clip-path`
- `solidYellow` mode for full yellow background (no split)
- Real or synthetic crests (circle with initials)
- Giant Moret italic score
- MVP with B&W photo + decorative number behind
- Stats strip (5 columns desktop, 2 mobile)
- Centered action buttons in footer
- Scroll cue (circular button with chevron)

