### 3. Sports Card Pattern

Standard card used throughout the app.

```tsx
<div className="bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/8 border-l-4 border-l-neon-yellow rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
  {/* Header */}
  <div className="px-5 sm:px-6 py-5 sm:py-6 border-b border-white/10 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-2">
    <div className="ole-eyebrow !text-neon-yellow">
      <span>Section Title</span>
    </div>
    <p className="text-white/55 uppercase" style={{
      fontFamily: 'var(--font-ui)',
      fontSize: '11px',
      letterSpacing: '0.22em',
      fontWeight: 600,
    }}>
      Descriptive subtitle
    </p>
  </div>

  {/* Body */}
  <div className="px-6 py-4">
    {/* Content */}
  </div>

  {/* Footer (optional) */}
  <div className="px-5 sm:px-6 pb-5 sm:pb-6 pt-2">
    <button className="w-full py-3 bg-neon-yellow text-black hover:bg-white">
      Primary CTA
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Anatomy:**
1. Background: `bg-[var(--color-card)]` (#242424)
2. General border: `border border-white/8` (subtle)
3. Signature border: `border-l-4 border-l-neon-yellow` (yellow left stripe)
4. Border-radius: `rounded-sm` (4px — sharp sports)
5. Internal dividers: `border-white/10`

