## ⚡ Micro-interactions

### Hover Effects
```tsx
// Buttons
hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]

// Icons
hover:scale-110 transition-transform

// Cards
hover:scale-[1.01] hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(253,225,0,0.15)]

// ChevronRight
hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform
```

### Animations (Framer Motion)

#### Card Entry
```tsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  transition={{ delay: 0.1 }}
>
  {/* Card */}
</motion.div>
```

#### Stagger List
```tsx
{items.map((item, idx) => (
  <motion.div
    key={item.id}
    initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12 }}
    animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
    transition={{ delay: 0.1 + idx * 0.04 }}
  >
    {/* Item */}
  </motion.div>
))}
```

#### Live Pulse (Live indicator)
```css
.live-dot {
  animation: ole-live-pulse 1.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes ole-live-pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.85); }
}
```

#### Hover Glow (Yellow)
```css
.ole-yellow-glow::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(
    circle at center,
    rgba(253, 225, 0, 0.15) 0%,
    transparent 70%
  );
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
}
.ole-yellow-glow:hover::before {
  opacity: 1;
}
```

