## 🛠️ Implementation Checklist

When implementing a new page or component:

### Layout Structure
- [ ] Use `DashboardGrid` + `DashboardSection` for responsive layout
- [ ] Apply `-mx-3 -mt-3 sm:-mx-4 sm:-mt-4 lg:-mx-8 lg:-mt-8` on full-bleed heroes
- [ ] Spacing between sections: `space-y-6` or `space-y-8` (24-32px)

### Cards/Panels
- [ ] Background: `bg-[var(--color-card)]`
- [ ] Border: `border border-white/8`
- [ ] Highlight: `border-l-4 border-l-neon-yellow`
- [ ] Border-radius: `rounded-sm` (4px)
- [ ] Dividers: `border-white/10`

### Typography
- [ ] Eyebrows: `font-ui`, `10-11px`, `uppercase`, `tracking-[0.22em]`, `text-neon-yellow`
- [ ] Headlines: `font-display`, `font-black`, `uppercase`, `tracking-wider`
- [ ] Large numbers: `font-serif-hero`, `italic`, `tabular-nums`
- [ ] Body: `font-sans`, `text-sm` or `text-xs`, `text-gray-400`

### Buttons
- [ ] Primary: `bg-neon-yellow text-black hover:bg-white`
- [ ] Outline: `bg-deep-black border border-white/15 hover:border-neon-yellow`
- [ ] Font: `font-display font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]`
- [ ] Size: `text-[11px] sm:text-[12px]`

### Colors
- [ ] Background: `bg-deep-black` (#0D0D0D)
- [ ] Cards: `bg-[var(--color-card)]` (#242424)
- [ ] Highlight: `text-neon-yellow` (#FDE100)
- [ ] Primary text: `text-white`
- [ ] Secondary text: `text-gray-400` or `text-white/55`

### Animations
- [ ] Cards: `motion.div` with `initial/animate` + progressive delay
- [ ] Hover: `transition-colors duration-200`
- [ ] Scale: `hover:scale-[1.01] active:scale-[0.99]`

