## 🎯 When to Use This Skill

Use this skill when:
- Implementing new pages or features in OLEFOOT
- Standardizing existing pages with the design system
- Creating new components that need to match the visual identity
- Reviewing UI/UX consistency across the app
- Designing hero sections, cards, buttons, or any visual element
- Ensuring responsive behavior matches the BVB-inspired aesthetic

**Always prioritize:**
1. Visual hierarchy (Druk → Moret → Inter)
2. Sharp, angular design (max 8px radius)
3. Yellow as intentional highlight
4. Generous spacing and breathing room
5. Subtle, coordinated motion
6. Cinematic, editorial feel

